# WordPress folder is read-only

- Never create, edit, delete, or rename files under `wordpress/`.
- When changing site content or behavior, edit the static site files instead (`index.html`, `about.html`, `services.html`, `contact.html`, `css/`, `js/`, etc.).
- If asked to change WordPress theme files, refuse and point to the matching static files unless the user explicitly overrides this rule for that request.
